# Copy this file to local.secrets.env and fill your real key.
# This file format is KEY=VALUE (no quotes required).
#
# Which backend Claude Code uses (optional — omit for Anthropic-style defaults):
# PC_DOCTOR_LLM_PROVIDER=anthropic
# PC_DOCTOR_LLM_PROVIDER=deepseek
#
# deepseek: sets ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL to DeepSeek’s gateway if you did not set it yourself.
# anthropic: removes ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL only when it still pointed at DeepSeek (switching back).
#
# --- Anthropic — remove or comment when using only DeepSeek ---
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-your-key-here
#
# --- DeepSeek via Claude Code (optional; Anthropic-compatible API) ---
# Get a key from the DeepSeek platform, then set the variables below per:
# https://api-docs.deepseek.com/guides/coding_agents#integrate-with-claude-code
# Example (models may change — follow the current DeepSeek guide):
# PC_DOCTOR_LLM_PROVIDER=deepseek
# ANTHROPIC_AUTH_TOKEN=your-deepseek-api-key
# With PC_DOCTOR_LLM_PROVIDER=deepseek you can omit ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL (defaults applied).
# Or set explicitly:
# ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL=https://api.deepseek.com/anthropic
# ANTHROPIC_MODEL=deepseek-v4-pro
# ANTHROPIC_DEFAULT_OPUS_MODEL=deepseek-v4-pro
# ANTHROPIC_DEFAULT_SONNET_MODEL=deepseek-v4-pro
# ANTHROPIC_DEFAULT_HAIKU_MODEL=deepseek-v4-flash
# CLAUDE_CODE_SUBAGENT_MODEL=deepseek-v4-flash
# CLAUDE_CODE_EFFORT_LEVEL=max
# If ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL points at DeepSeek and AUTH_TOKEN is unset, install.bat copies
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY to ANTHROPIC_AUTH_TOKEN for Claude Code when needed.
